e0943025038d7f7ea5a373c97082d79ea10c8b802760ccc93a6640dd6b8c1ee871b103bf428791acc9be283b19707ecaadc36db81a3c87e6103fd612e9c12dc0  fix-loongarch64-build.patch
"
